------WebKitFormBoundary--
### LIST FILES IN BUCKET
GET {{FilesUrl}}/{{BucketName}}

### GET FILE METADATA (You would need to update the fileId defination above to a value produced when you upload a file  )
GET {{FilesUrl}}/{{BucketName}}/files/{{fileId}}

#### DOWNLOAD FILE
GET {{FilesUrl}}/{{BucketId}}/files/{{fileId}}/download



### UPDATE FILE METADATA
PATCH {{FilesUrl}}/{{BucketId}}/files/{{fileId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "metadata": {
    "description": "Updated document",
    "tags": "important,archive",
    "modified_by": "user123"
  }
}

### COPY FILE
POST {{FilesUrl}}/{{BucketId}}/files/{{fileId}}/copy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "destination_bucket": "test-bucket1",
  "new_key": "copied-example.png"
}


### MOVE FILE
POST {{FilesUrl}}/files/{{BucketId}}/files/{{fileId}}/move
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "destination_bucket": "archive-bucket",
  "new_key": "archived-example.png"
}

### DELETE FILE
DELETE {{FilesUrl}}/{{BucketId}}/files/{{fileId}}



 


